   <div id="sub03"> 
    <div class="sub03_txt1 txtstyle">
     ASUS GamePlus lets you get more out of your game. Four crosshair options make sure you’re always on the mark; while an onscreen timer on the left of the display helps you track elapsed game time. There’s even a frames per second (FPS)* counter to let you know how smooth the game is running.
     <br>
     <br> 
     <p>*only available on MG278Q.</p>
